examples.en: A male duck is a drake.
The whole idea is diabolically simple, notes Drake.
examples.ru: Вся затея предельно проста, отмечает Дрейк.

examples.en: Drake was consumed by the idea of sailing into the Pacific.

examples.en: Drake was admitted into the club in 1997.
